                      <p align="justify">
                        <strong>IELTS:</strong> A MINIMUM SCORE OF 5 IELTS IS REQUIRED FROM INDIAN STUDENTS WHO WISH TO
                        APPLY FOR A STUDY VISA FOR IRELAND.<br>

                        <strong>TOEFL: </strong>A MIMIMUM SCORE OF 173 IS REQUIRED FROM INDIAN STUDENTS WHO WISH TO
                        APPLY FOR A STUDY VISA FOR IRELAND.</p><br>

